# 3D Solar System

## Features Implemented
- 3D simulation using **Three.js**
- Sun at the center with **8 orbiting planets**
- Each planet has its own **speed, color, size**
- **Speed control sliders** (real-time)
- **Pause/Resume** animation
- **Dark/Light mode** toggle
- **Tooltips** on planet hover
- **Click to zoom camera**
- **Starfield background**

## Technologies Used
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Three.js (via CDN)

## How to Run the Project
1. Download or extract the `.zip` file
2. Open `index.html` in Chrome or any modern browser
3. No installation or server required

